responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "613EE0F94A924C4C218DB1A1E24663D3", "Deliver us this immortality and riches untold and we shall serve together forver your bold. She gazed upon them with eyes glowing bright grinning and shooting forth a beam of light. In agony and pain the tauroxians were reborn, turned into gold from hoof to horn. The curse of the tyrants greed and bloodlust now goes. Off to other worlds and souls to dispose.")
